jeigen
Class SparseMatrixLil

java.lang.Object
  jeigen.SparseMatrixLil

public class SparseMatrixLil
extends java.lang.Object

Stores a sparse matrix as row,column,value triplets. SparseMatrixLil is faster if a lot of the matrix values are zero. When the matrix is fully dense, DenseMatrix is faster.
